name: Striker Number Nine
overview: An arcade style footy\soccer game, Striker Number 9 gives you the chance to prove how good a soccer player you really are! Test your skills in over a dozen grueling, joystick-breaking sessions, to see if you are up to the first team! Test your stamina on the track, your aim with penalty practice, your teamwork in the passing practice and over 10 more addictive games! Striker is packed full of variety and playability to keep you coming back for more.
